Pixas is an Open Source ActionScript engine, which enables programmers to build isometric pixel Flash Applications with pure ActionScript3. With Pixas you can easily add isometric pixel elements like brick, cube, pyramid, map layer to your applications.

Showcase - Pixas Editor: http://risonhuang.com/pixas_editor.html

Showcase - Uncle Big's Adventure: http://risonhuang.com/uncle.html

Check out more informations about examples, tutorials and documents at here: http://risonhuang.com/pixas.html

Follow Pixas_Engine on twitter: https://twitter.com/pixas_engine

